This paper deals with the design of autonomous systems operating in uncertain environments, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses decision-making and control, which are relevant to machine learning (cs.LG) and software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper presents a computational architecture for problem-solving, which is relevant to systems and control (cs.SY).
